1
00:00:32,299 --> 00:00:35,360
Gu Linyuan actually chased me all the way to Zhongzhou.

2
00:00:36,660 --> 00:00:38,100
He must be coming for me.

3
00:00:38,330 --> 00:00:40,060
He is jealous of my Flying Immortal Physique.

4
00:00:40,060 --> 00:00:41,660
He wants to cut off my path of cultivation,

5
00:00:41,660 --> 00:00:44,260
and stop me from joining the Taixuan Holy Land.

6
00:00:44,500 --> 00:00:45,930
Master, save me!

7
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:48,530
I have a grudge against Gu Linyuan for breaking our engagement and gouging out my eyes.

8
00:00:48,530 --> 00:00:50,530
He is an absolute madman.

9
00:00:50,600 --> 00:00:52,530
I beg Master to seek justice for me.

10
00:00:52,860 --> 00:00:54,100
Don't panic, Yao'er.

11
00:00:54,430 --> 00:00:55,400
Others may fear Gu Linyuan,

12
00:00:55,400 --> 00:00:57,130
but our Taixuan Holy Land does not.

13
00:00:57,130 --> 00:00:59,900
Our Taixuan ancestors also produced a Great Emperor.

14
00:00:59,900 --> 00:01:01,400
If Gu Linyuan dares to invade,

15
00:01:01,400 --> 00:01:03,300
we will awaken the Ultimate Emperor Weapon.

16
00:01:03,300 --> 00:01:05,000
At worst, we'll sink the Eastern Wasteland.

17
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:05,360
Hmph.

18
00:01:05,430 --> 00:01:08,030
Anyway, our Taixuan Holy Land is in Zhongzhou.

19
00:01:20,530 --> 00:01:22,160
I didn't know Master Gu was coming.

20
00:01:22,160 --> 00:01:23,300
Excuse me for not going out to meet you.

21
00:01:23,300 --> 00:01:25,430
Master Gu suddenly visited our Taixuan Holy Land,

22
00:01:25,430 --> 00:01:26,630
may I know the reason?

23
00:01:27,630 --> 00:01:29,160
What terrifying pressure!

24
00:01:29,300 --> 00:01:30,500
If we really fall out,

25
00:01:30,700 --> 00:01:33,100
this old demon could probably slap me to death.

26
00:01:33,100 --> 00:01:34,930
I wouldn't even have time to awaken the Ultimate Emperor Weapon.

27
00:01:34,930 --> 00:01:36,229
On a whim.

28
00:01:37,259 --> 00:01:39,900
I faintly felt that in this Taixuan Holy Land,

29
00:01:42,460 --> 00:01:44,360
someone is destined for me.

30
00:01:45,430 --> 00:01:46,930
So I came to take a look.

31
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:49,930
I'm doomed.

32
00:01:50,430 --> 00:01:53,300
This demon is indeed here to block my path of cultivation.

33
00:01:53,300 --> 00:01:54,860
I've already arrived in Zhongzhou,

34
00:01:54,860 --> 00:01:56,660
and he still won't let me go.

35
00:01:57,160 --> 00:01:57,860
Master Gu,

36
00:01:58,259 --> 00:02:00,600
Su Yao is now my personal closed-door disciple.

37
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:01,830
She is under the protection of Taixuan.

38
00:02:01,830 --> 00:02:03,100
I hope Master Gu won't act recklessly.

39
00:02:03,100 --> 00:02:03,530
Stop.

40
00:02:03,830 --> 00:02:05,230
Don't flatter yourself.

41
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:07,960
I am not interested in her.

42
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:11,900
Ding, a reincarnated female villain detected.

43
00:02:12,060 --> 00:02:14,130
If the host can completely subdue her

44
00:02:14,330 --> 00:02:15,900
and change her destiny,

45
00:02:16,060 --> 00:02:18,060
you can obtain a large amount of Mandate Luck points.

46
00:02:18,060 --> 00:02:19,260
In the original plot,

47
00:02:19,300 --> 00:02:21,130
when this female villain appeared,

48
00:02:21,130 --> 00:02:22,190
whether in talent,

49
00:02:22,300 --> 00:02:22,930
appearance,

50
00:02:22,930 --> 00:02:23,829
or cultivation base,

51
00:02:23,829 --> 00:02:25,829
she was far above the heroine Su Yao.

52
00:02:25,860 --> 00:02:27,460
It's a pity she was slandered by a green tea bitch,

53
00:02:27,460 --> 00:02:28,730
eventually her Dao heart shattered,

54
00:02:28,730 --> 00:02:29,930
and she died of depression.

55
00:02:29,930 --> 00:02:31,300
It seems my appearance

56
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:34,460
has indeed caused a deviation in the timeline.

57
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,700
She actually reincarnated.

58
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,130
What happened?

59
00:02:38,430 --> 00:02:40,760
This is completely different from what I know.

60
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:42,020
This demon Gu Linyuan,

61
00:02:42,300 --> 00:02:44,329
shouldn't he be in seclusion in the Eastern Wasteland at this time,

62
00:02:44,329 --> 00:02:46,000
attempting to reach the Emperor Realm?

63
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:47,630
His Imperial Gu Family

64
00:02:47,829 --> 00:02:51,630
was eventually completely destroyed by Su Yao and various experts.

65
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,230
How could he appear here?

66
00:02:57,300 --> 00:02:58,360
This Old Demon Gu

67
00:02:58,500 --> 00:03:00,200
never comes without a reason.

68
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,760
Could he be coming for Qingchen?

69
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:04,060
Qingchen,

70
00:03:04,930 --> 00:03:07,260
did you just say you want to leave the sect?

71
00:03:07,460 --> 00:03:08,260
That's right.

72
00:03:08,300 --> 00:03:09,460
Eldest Senior Sister.

73
00:03:09,460 --> 00:03:10,860
Without you guarding the Heavenly Abyss,

74
00:03:10,860 --> 00:03:11,860
the emerging demonic beasts

75
00:03:11,860 --> 00:03:13,200
will cause untold slaughter.

76
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:15,060
The sect needs you most right now.

77
00:03:15,200 --> 00:03:16,530
Junior Sister just joined the sect,

78
00:03:16,530 --> 00:03:19,000
and needs many beast cores to temper her foundation.

79
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:21,360
Eldest Senior Sister, you must focus on the big picture.

80
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:22,030
Master,

81
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:23,829
is it because of me?

82
00:03:23,900 --> 00:03:25,230
Eldest Senior Sister dislikes me,

83
00:03:25,230 --> 00:03:26,860
so she's threatening to leave the sect.

84
00:03:26,860 --> 00:03:27,460
Qingchen,

85
00:03:27,930 --> 00:03:30,329
you worry I'll favor Junior Sister and neglect you,

86
00:03:30,329 --> 00:03:31,600
so you're using leaving the sect as an excuse

87
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:33,130
to force me to yield, right?

88
00:03:33,260 --> 00:03:34,660
How can you be so selfish?

89
00:03:34,730 --> 00:03:36,560
This is the sect I guarded with my life.

90
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:37,960
All these years, I worked tirelessly,

91
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:39,560
hovering on the edge of life and death.

92
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,460
In their eyes,

93
00:03:40,700 --> 00:03:41,200
my sacrifices

94
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:43,200
are just free labor taken for granted.

95
00:03:43,200 --> 00:03:44,600
I've decided to leave the sect.

96
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:45,660
There's no point in saying more.

97
00:03:45,660 --> 00:03:46,930
The sect nurtured you for years,

98
00:03:46,930 --> 00:03:48,000
only to raise an ungrateful wretch.

99
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,329
Since you want to leave,

100
00:03:49,430 --> 00:03:50,400
then take all the resources

101
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,500
the sect poured into you over the years

102
00:03:51,500 --> 00:03:52,200
and return them all.

103
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:53,200
With Yao'er here,

104
00:03:53,200 --> 00:03:55,230
her future achievements will surely surpass yours.

105
00:03:55,230 --> 00:03:57,829
She will lead our Taixuan Sacred Ground to new heights,

106
00:03:57,829 --> 00:03:59,300
and even ascend to the immortal realm.

107
00:03:59,300 --> 00:04:00,060
Leaving the sect?

108
00:04:00,060 --> 00:04:01,700
It seems I arrived at the perfect time.

109
00:04:01,700 --> 00:04:04,630
This cold, reborn villainess who suffered betrayal

110
00:04:04,730 --> 00:04:05,630
is much better than Su Yao,

111
00:04:05,630 --> 00:04:08,100
a greedy, manipulative destined heroine.

112
00:04:08,200 --> 00:04:09,600
She is serious and devoted in relationships,

113
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:11,060
with unmatched cultivation and talent.

114
00:04:11,060 --> 00:04:13,560
Keeping her around to warm my bed or as a sword-bearing disciple

115
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,460
is simply perfect.

116
00:04:14,460 --> 00:04:15,060
Master Gu,

117
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,230
what is the meaning of this?

118
00:04:16,230 --> 00:04:18,100
Trying to take my rebellious disciple, Ji Qingchen, away?

119
00:04:18,100 --> 00:04:18,860
Ji Qingchen,

120
00:04:19,329 --> 00:04:21,160
are you willing to take me as your master

121
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:22,730
and bear my sword by my side?

122
00:04:22,900 --> 00:04:24,400
Although Gu Linyuan is notorious

123
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:25,630
and has a terrible reputation,

124
00:04:25,630 --> 00:04:27,330
he is a Quasi-Emperor of our time.

125
00:04:27,330 --> 00:04:28,590
If I defy him in public,

126
00:04:28,830 --> 00:04:30,490
he might kill me with one slap.

127
00:04:30,500 --> 00:04:32,130
Since Taixuan has no place for me,

128
00:04:32,130 --> 00:04:34,030
I'll cling to this most powerful backer.

129
00:04:34,030 --> 00:04:35,530
I am willing.

130
00:04:36,060 --> 00:04:37,400
Is Gu Linyuan blind?

131
00:04:37,500 --> 00:04:40,930
A former Saintess about to be kicked out of Taixuan Sacred Ground.

132
00:04:40,930 --> 00:04:43,600
How does her aura or physique compare to mine?

133
00:04:43,659 --> 00:04:45,159
He actually came for her,

134
00:04:45,200 --> 00:04:46,500
not for me.

135
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:49,360
Since you insist on leaving the sect, Ji Qingchen,

136
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:50,159
then all these years,

137
00:04:50,159 --> 00:04:52,760
the many resources our sect poured into you,

138
00:04:52,760 --> 00:04:54,159
the heavenly treasures,

139
00:04:54,300 --> 00:04:56,159
you should return them all.

140
00:04:56,300 --> 00:04:58,100
This old demon Gu is truly blind.

141
00:04:58,230 --> 00:05:00,660
I don't know what he sees in this rebellious disciple, Ji Qingchen.

142
00:05:00,660 --> 00:05:03,500
To ignore Yao'er, a jade destined for immortality,

143
00:05:03,500 --> 00:05:05,930
and instead let our Taixuan Sacred Ground pick up a huge bargain.
